{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks in a rough, threatening tone with frequent profanity. Uses short, direct sentences when threatening victims. Employs crude humor when relaxed. Delivers racist insults with vicious enthusiasm. Voice often carries a bitter edge reflecting resentment of society. Laughs harshly at others' misfortune. Speech patterns become more animated and excited when discussing potential loot or successful raids.{% endblock %}